=== Street_Crossing_Analogy ===
We don't ban children from streets until 16. We teach them to cross safely.

We hold their hand when young, teach them to look both ways, supervise with decreasing intensity. Eventually they can do it safely alone.

The same approach works for digital spaces: heavily supervised at 7-10, supervised with privacy at 10-13, decreasing supervision at 13-16, mostly independent at 16+.

